question: Lōa-lâi ê bu̍t-îⁿ hō-chòe 'BC2_64' ê khò͘-sǹg hē-tóng, sím-mih chiat-hông hō·-sóan ê hong-hoat bē-su cheng-siâⁿ khah kē ê tiāⁿ-chòe?
LASSO regression feature selection' 这一种方法，用予所有 forecasting settings 的平均 exogenous variables 是多少？
'BC3_28' ê hong-sìng thiau-kiàn, ēng siōng-chē gōa-chè só͘-chāi gōa-chè ê hong-hoat ê sún-sit phiah-sò͘ sī siáⁿ-chē?
BC1_64'ê kiat-su-bīn lāi-bīn, cheng-ka gōa-lâi hōe-chū-sò͘ ê sò͘-liōng ē-tàng kò͘-tēng thè-thian sêng-chek (iā-chiū-sī kàng-ke sió-tò͘)? Chòe chi̍t ê kán-té ê hun-sek.
answer: Bōe, bô chi̍t ê kò͘-tēng ê koan-hē. Tī 'BC1_64' ê kiat-su-bīn lāi-bīn, 'Correlation-Based Selection' iōng 3 ê hōe-chū-sò͘ lâi tit-tio̍h 14.11 ê sió-tò͘, 'LASSO regression' iā iōng 3 ê hōe-chū-sò͘ tān-sī ū khah koân ê 14.55 ê sió-tò͘. 'Forward Feature Selection NP' iōng chin tōa ê sò͘-liōng ê hōe-chū-sò͘ (28) chin khoài lâi tit-tio̍h 9.16 ê sió-tò͘. Chiah-ê jīn-ûi kóng thè-thian ê hōe-chū-sò͘ ê sò͘-liōng ē-tàng khah hó, tān-sī siâng-tō͘ chiap ê hōe-chū-sò͘ bōe-tàng hō͘ sêng-chek kò͘-tēng thè-thian.

question: La̍k-miâ ê sî-ta̍t chè-tōaⁿ hong-sek, hō͘ 'BC3_64' chè-tōaⁿ ê koân-pái chhiau-kóe 15 ê sò͘-jī?
Tī 'Forward Feature Selection NP' ê só͘-chāi ke-hō（settings）lāi-bīn, ū pau-koat ê exogenu kap choân-pō͘ exogenu ê chi̍t-pí-lu̍t sī tī 'BC1_64' ê setting ū chi̍t-pō͘-hun ê chi̍t-pí-lu̍t sī jin-nó-hō?

Nā-sī ū chi̍t-ê sò͘-kì thiâu-lí chhò-gō͘ chōa-chiâⁿ 'BC2_28' siat-tēng ê só͘-ū chhò-gō͘ phō-pái lóng pí kì-lo̍k ê sò͘-jī koh-khah kē 2.5 tiám, 'chū-chú tū-hêng tû-khì-hoat sióⁿ-sò͘ chū-hāng soán-ti̍k' ê sin chhò-gō͘ ē-sī siáⁿ-mih?

Tī kāi ê feature selection phương-sek tiong, só͘ lia̍t chhut ê variable siâⁿ-khuán chē ê, nā kā tùi chē-chē ê forecasting setting ê variable siâⁿ-khuán (siang-tōa hām siang-sió ê chha) lâi khòaⁿ, che hō͘-chhoán kiâⁿ-chīn siáte-tē-tāi (instability) ê sī sím-mih?

'LASSO regression feature selection' chit ê hong-sò, 'BC3_28' ê siâⁿ-sit ê sêng-sò͘ sī chi̍t-ê gōa-khì. Tī kāng chit-ê hong-sò ê khǹg tùi lēng-gōa ê hong-sò lâi koan-hē, i ê tūi-èng ê gōa-lâi sò͘-liōng sī ch like-e?
answer: BC3_28' ê tēng-gī, LASSO chhiúⁿ siâⁿ-sit sī 28.79, iā-ūi chin koân, chit-ê iā-ūi siōng koân ê gōa-lâi sòaⁿ-sò͘ (16) choán-tāi chit-ê hong-sò. Chit-ê siâⁿ-sò͘ khah chē chē lâi kî-tha ê tēng-gī, tùi 0 kàu 10 ê sòaⁿ-sò͘. Chit-ê chhut-hiān chi̍t-ê khó-lêng ê būn-tê, LASSO hong-sò chhah chi̍t-ê tōa, chiū-kńg chin bái-e ê liân-kiat, chūi-jiân hō͘ chit-ê te̍k-sû ê tōa-kái-sî chêng-khêng.

question: Tùi 'Bô gōa-chú-liāu' ê ki-chún-sòaⁿ, chòe sím-mih kiám-giām ê sî phòe-tìⁿ ê tiāu-chéng tùi 'BC1' kàu 'BC2' liáu-āu kàu 'BC3' ê sî, chun-chiap kiám-giām tùi phòe-tìⁿ ê tiāu-chéng ê chha-chòe phòe-tìⁿ ê hêng-thài sī chn̄g-sòaⁿ?
answer: Tùi 'Bô gōa-chú-liāu' ê ki-chún-sòaⁿ lâi kóng, hêng-tōaⁿ sī ū chi̍t ê bêng-hián ê tōe-sè. I khai-sí tī BC1 ê tiāu-chéng sī ū tiong-téng ê chha-chòe tiāu-chha (11.14, 13.65). Hêng-tōaⁿ tit-tio̍h tōa-tōa ê kái-siān tī BC2 ê tiāu-chéng, in ū siōng-kē ê chha-chòe (3.75, 9.08). Chòe-āu, chha-chòe koh teh tōa-tōa ê tōa-tōa tī BC3 ê tiāu-chéng (17.53, 9.06), BC3_64 sī chòe-koân ê chha-chòe tōa-tōa lâi kóng chiap-chhiáⁿ. Chúi-bîn lâi kóng, chhiáng-chòe ê bô͘-hêng sī siōng-hó teh hùn-chiap BC2 ê tiāu-kiāⁿ.

question: Tī 'LASSO regression feature selection' kap 'Forward Feature Selection NP' chi-kan, Sí-liâu 'BC2_64' siat-tēng ê hāng-bo̍k, lán ê hē-thóng saⁿ-chiáⁿ ê kó͘-sò͘ koh-khah kē?
answer: 'Forward Feature Selection NP' ê kó͘-sò͘ (2.9) koh-khah kē tī 'LASSO regression feature selection' (5.73) koan-î BC2_64 siat-tēng.
